snippet.title: Supercharge Your Marketing with Google Cloud (Cloud Next ‘19 UK)
snippet.description:
Your company has lots of valuable marketing data, but it’s spread across many systems and teams. With Cloud, you can bring this data together in one place so you can better analyze and activate it. In this session, you’ll learn about new GCP tools for marketers and hear directly from brands who are using them to solve use cases like audience segmentation, purchase prediction, and measuring lifetime value. You’ll walk away with an understanding of how to adopt technology that transforms the way your company delivers marketing campaigns and customer experiences.

Session ID: SMAI100
Speaker(s):
Kimberly Kelly, Senior Solutions Consultant, Google Cloud 0:10
Atul Kumar, Director, Product Management, Google Cloud 12:29
Amber Grubben, Digital Data Manager, Rituals 18:29
Guy Hancox, Group Head, Data Science, Waitrose & Partners 29:24
Andrew Leigh, Analytics Manager, Waitrose & Partners 29:24
